Step 6ï¸âƒ£ Verify Installation
python -c "import numpy; print(numpy.__version__)"
Step 7ï¸âƒ£ Save Dependencies (Best Practice)
pip freeze > requirements.txt

Used later in:

CI/CD

Docker

Kubernetes

Step 8ï¸âƒ£ Deactivate When Done
deactivate
ğŸ”¹ Key Commands Summary (Cheat Sheet)
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
python -m pip install <package>
pip freeze > requirements.txt
deactivate
ğŸ”¹ Common Mistakes (Avoid)

